                            <comment id="13869655" author="iamaleksey" created="Mon, 13 Jan 2014 16:12:36 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;Also, would it be possible to get some INFO-level logging (like HH has) on batchlog replay while we&apos;re here?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sure. What do you have in mind?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
